Windows packet sniffers and network monitors
--------------------------------------------
CommView: https://www.tamos.com/products/commview/
Cain & Abel: Discontinued
Wireshark: https://www.wireshark.org/#download
Net Tools 5: https://www.softpedia.com/get/Network-Tools/Misc-Networking-Tools/Net-Tools.shtml
netstat: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Netstat
LANC Remastered: https://sourceforge.net/projects/lanc-remastered-ip/
(Port Scanner) nmap/zenmap: https://nmap.org/zenmap/

Linux packet sniffers and network monitors
------------------------------------------
tcpdump: https://www.tcpdump.org/
iftop: http://www.ex-parrot.com/pdw/iftop/
nload: https://www.tecmint.com/nload-monitor-linux-network-traffic-bandwidth-usage/
netstat: https://linux.die.net/man/8/netstat 
(Port Scanner) nmap: https://nmap.org/
